Citation.sTitle: Solubility of Bromoderivatives C60Brn (n = 6, 8, 24) in 1-Chloronaphthalene and 1-Bromonaphthalene in the Temperature Range (10 to 60) deg C
Citation.sAbstract: On the basis of the isothermal saturated method in ampules, the solubility of bromoderivatives C60Brn (n = 6, 8, 24) in 1-chloronaphthalene and 1-bromonaphthalene in the (10 to 60) deg C temperature range was determined. The temperature dependencies of solubility and density are presented and characterized, and the compositions of equilibrium solid phases are determined.
